        <div class="verdict">✓ Updated April 2026</div>

        <p>Roofing is one of the most software-specific trades. You deal with insurance adjusters, aerial measurement tools, storm chasers, material ordering, and rapid job turnover — often multiple roofs per week. Generic project management tools miss this. Roofing-specific software was built for it.</p>

        <p>This guide covers the best options from purpose-built roofing platforms to broader construction management tools that work well for roofers.</p>

